Package smarthome.domain.repository

Interface ISensorRepository

All Superinterfaces:
IRepository<SensorId, Sensor>
All Known Implementing Classes:
SensorRepositoryJPAImpl, SensorRepositoryMemImpl, SensorRepositorySpringDataImpl
public interface ISensorRepository extends IRepository<SensorId,Sensor>
The ISensorRepository interface represents a repository for managing Sensor entities. It provides methods to save, retrieve, and manipulate Sensor objects.
